Summary: Better diagnostics from file transfer backends
Class: wish
Difficulty: fun
Priority: medium
Content-type: text/x-html-body

<p>
There should be better diagnostics surrounding the choice between the
SCP and SFTP backends in the file transfer utilities (PSCP, PSFTP). In
particular, it should be possible to tell easily which of the backends
was used from the `-v' output.
